{"type": "article", "id": 28057, "title": "餐具滤干架", "description": "", "date": "2016-06-12T06:57:16Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 3, "praise_count": 39, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702142446654YSDyPX2VchAC7.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>          </p>\n<p>看腻了单调的餐具晾干架？<a href=\"http://www.bertussidesign.com/site/includes/index.php\">Bertussi Design</a> 为 Martiplast 设计的 <a href=\"http://www.ou.com.br/Produtos/Organizar/Sobre%20a%20Pia/751#.V1wV66N95p9\">Discovery</a> 凭借它优雅的曲线让人过目难忘。它的高低结构借鉴了建筑和车辆的流线型外观，一方面提升了空气流动加快晾干过程，另一方面也可以晾干刀叉和筷子，同时摆放各类不同的餐具，既美观又实用。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702142443hisnfxTGyuqNJlOv.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"0.98333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702142444IwY6WduVjgBlSHPK.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.63166667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702142444FwAPVKxEg1kqOZId.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.77833333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021424450Gc4tw8uoIl6BTY2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n"}